{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775887226880,"sessionID":"ses_284dfe4edffeXF09uj2DLyG8WE","part":{"id":"prt_d7b2095170017REDxwWTgh4kSr","messageID":"msg_d7b208c7e0015hVnbwLgmu0TNd","sessionID":"ses_284dfe4edffeXF09uj2DLyG8WE","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b8d33aaa46374849aea78be044e9bb25","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 Specification\n2: \n3: ## Module: client-go\n4: \n5: ### ClientSet\n6: \n7: #### ClientSet Definition\n8: \n9: ```go\n10: type Interface interface {\n11:     Runtime() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n12:     Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n13: }\n14: ```\n15: \n16: #### RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n17: \n18: ```go\n19: type RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n20:     RESTClient() rest.Interface\n21:     AgentRuntimes(agentRuntime string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n22:     CodeInterpreters(codeInterpreter string) CodeInterpreterInterface\n23: }\n24: ```\n25: \n26: ### AgentRuntime Client\n27: \n28: #### AgentRuntimeInterface\n29: \n30: ```go\n31: type AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n32:     Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n33:     Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n34:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n35:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n36:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n37:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n38:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n39:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n40:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n41: }\n42: ```\n43: \n44: #### AgentRuntime Methods\n45: \n46: **Create**\n47: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.CreateOptions`\n48: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n49: - **Description**: Create a new AgentRuntime resource\n50: \n51: **Update**\n52: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n53: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n54: - **Description**: Update an existing AgentRuntime resource\n55: \n56: **UpdateStatus**\n57: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n58: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n59: - **Description**: Update the status subresource of an AgentRuntime\n60: \n61: **Delete**\n62: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.DeleteOptions`\n63: - **Returns**: `error`\n64: - **Description**: Delete an AgentRuntime resource by name\n65: \n66: **Get**\n67: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.GetOptions`\n68: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n69: - **Description**: Get an AgentRuntime resource by name\n70: \n71: **List**\n72: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n73: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList`, `error`\n74: - **Description**: List AgentRuntime resources\n75: \n76: **Watch**\n77: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n78: - **Returns**: `watch.Interface`, `error`\n79: - **Description**: Watch for AgentRuntime resource changes\n80: \n81: **Patch**\n82: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `pt types.PatchType`, `data []byte`, `opts metav1.PatchOptions`, `subresources ...string`\n83: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n84: - **Description**: Patch an AgentRuntime resource\n85: \n86: ### CodeInterpreter Client\n87: \n88: #### CodeInterpreterInterface\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: type CodeInterpreterInterface interface {\n92:     Create(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n93:     Update(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n94:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n95:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n96:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n97:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n98:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList, error)\n99:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n100:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n101: }\n102: ```\n103: \n104: #### CodeInterpreter Methods\n105: \n106: **Create**\n107: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `opts metav1.CreateOptions`\n108: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n109: - **Description**: Create a new CodeInterpreter resource\n110: \n111: **Update**\n112: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n113: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n114: - **Description**: Update an existing CodeInterpreter resource\n115: \n116: **UpdateStatus**\n117: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n118: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n119: - **Description**: Update the status subresource of a CodeInterpreter\n120: \n121: **Delete**\n122: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.DeleteOptions`\n123: - **Returns**: `error`\n124: - **Description**: Delete a CodeInterpreter resource by name\n125: \n126: **Get**\n127: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.GetOptions`\n128: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n129: - **Description**: Get a CodeInterpreter resource by name\n130: \n131: **List**\n132: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n133: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList`, `error`\n134: - **Description**: List CodeInterpreter resources\n135: \n136: **Watch**\n137: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n138: - **Returns**: `watch.Interface`, `error`\n139: - **Description**: Watch for CodeInterpreter resource changes\n140: \n141: **Patch**\n142: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `pt types.PatchType`, `data []byte`, `opts metav1.PatchOptions`, `subresources ...string`\n143: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n144: - **Description**: Patch a CodeInterpreter resource\n145: \n146: ### Informer\n147: \n148: #### AgentRuntimeInformer\n149: \n150: ```go\n151: type AgentRuntimeInformer interface {\n152:     Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n153:     Lister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n154: }\n155: ```\n156: \n157: #### CodeInterpreterInformer\n158: \n159: ```go\n160: type CodeInterpreterInformer interface {\n161:     Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n162:     Lister() runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister\n163: }\n164: ```\n165: \n166: ### Lister\n167: \n168: #### AgentRuntimeLister\n169: \n170: ```go\n171: type AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n172:     List(selector labels.Selector) (ret []*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, err error)\n173:     AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n174:     AgentRuntimeListerExpansion\n175: }\n176: ```\n177: \n178: #### CodeInterpreterLister\n179: \n180: ```go\n181: type CodeInterpreterLister interface {\n182:     List(selector labels.Selector) (ret []*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, err error)\n183:     CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister\n184:     CodeInterpreterListerExpansion\n185: }\n186: ```\n187: \n188: ## Common Types\n189: \n190: ### API Verbs\n191: \n192: Common verbs for API operations:\n193: - `create` - Create a resource\n194: - `update` - Update a resource\n195: - `delete` - Delete a resource\n196: - `get` - Get a single resource\n197: - `list` - List multiple resources\n198: - `watch` - Watch for resource changes\n199: - `patch` - Patch a resource\n200: \n201: ### Context\n202: \n203: All client methods accept a `context.Context` for:\n204: - Request cancellation\n205: - Timeout control\n206: - Request-scoped values\n207: \n208: ### Error Handling\n209: \n210: All client methods return `error` for:\n211: - Network errors\n212: - API errors\n213: - Validation errors\n214: - Authentication/authorization errors\n215: \n216: ## Best Practices\n217: \n218: - Always provide context to client methods\n219: - Use proper error handling\n220: - Implement retry logic for transient failures\n221: - Use Listers for read-only operations when possible\n222: - Use Informers for event-driven workflows\n223: - Clean up resources properly (e.g., stop informers)\n224: - Use proper timeouts for long-running operations\n\n(End of file - total 224 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 Specification\n\n## Module: client-go\n\n### ClientSet\n\n#### ClientSet Definition\n\n```go\ntype Interface interface {\n    Runtime() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n    Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n}\n```\n\n#### RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n\n```go\ntype RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n    RESTClient() rest.Interface","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/spec.md","time":{"start":1775887226867,"end":1775887226878}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775887226883,"sessionID":"ses_284dfe4edffeXF09uj2DLyG8WE","part":{"id":"prt_d7b2097d5001dKb2mljqWLlGEt","messageID":"msg_d7b208c7e0015hVnbwLgmu0TNd","sessionID":"ses_284dfe4edffeXF09uj2DLyG8WE","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-c9a7681741a345d981207c78b570e337","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-035: client-go 类型客户端生成\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube 平台生成基于 Kubernetes client-go 的类型化客户端库，提供对自定义资源（AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter 等）的强类型 API 访问能力，支持 CRUD 操作、Watch 机制和 Informer 模式。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: client-go 类型客户端是 AgentCube 平台开发者工具链的核心组成部分，旨在：\n10: \n11: 1. **类型安全** - 提供编译时类型检查，避免运行时错误\n12: 2. **开发效率** - 简化 Kubernetes API 调用，提供简洁的开发体验\n13: 3. **标准化接口** - 遵循 Kubernetes client-go 最佳实践和约定\n14: 4. **高性能** - 支持高效的 Watch 和 Informer 机制\n15: 5. **可维护性** - 自动生成客户端代码，与 CRD 定义保持同步\n16: \n17: ## Module\n18: \n19: `client-go` - Go 客户端库\n20: \n21: ## Language\n22: \n23: Go\n24: \n25: ## Size\n26: \n27: L\n28: \n29: ## Scope\n30: \n31: ### In Scope\n32: \n33: 1. **ClientSet 生成**\n34:    - AgentRuntime client\n35:    - CodeInterpreter client\n36:    - 支持所有 Kubernetes API verbs (get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete)\n37: \n38: 2. **Typed Client**\n39:    - Namespace-scoped operations\n40:    - Cluster-scoped operations (如需要)\n41:    - 支持子资源 (status, scale)\n42: \n43: 3. **Informer 集成**\n44:    - AgentRuntime informer\n45:    - CodeInterpreter informer\n46:    - 事件处理器支持\n47:    - 缓存机制\n48: \n49: 4. **Lister 支持**\n50:    - AgentRuntime lister\n51:    - CodeInterpreter lister\n52:    - 高效的只读访问\n53: \n54: 5. **代码生成工具**\n55:    - code-generator 配置\n56:    - 自定义代码生成脚本\n57:    - 自动化文档生成\n58: \n59: ### Out of Scope\n60: \n61: - 其他语言的客户端（Python、Java 等）\n62: - 跨平台的客户端生成\n63: - gRPC 客户端生成\n64: - REST API 直接调用封装\n65: - CLI 工具集成\n66: \n67: ## Impact Analysis\n68: \n69: ### Components Impacted\n70: \n71: 1. **Controller Manager**\n72:    - 需要使用生成的客户端管理 AgentRuntime\n73:    - 需要 Informer 监听资源变更\n74: \n75: 2. **Workload Manager**\n76:    - 需要使用生成的客户端创建和管理 AgentRuntime\n77:    - 需要访问 AgentRuntime status\n78: \n79: 3. **外部工具和脚本**\n80:    - 需要使用客户端进行资源操作\n81:    - 需要 Watch 机制监听资源事件\n82: \n83: ### Dependencies\n84: \n85: - **Go 1.19+**: 客户端库开发语言\n86: - **Kubernetes 1.20+**: API 兼容性\n87: - **k8s.io/code-generator**: 代码生成工具\n88: - **k8s.io/client-go**: Kubernetes 客户端库基础\n89: \n90: ### Breaking Changes\n91: \n92: 无破坏性变更。客户端库是新增的 Go 模块。\n93: \n94: ## Design Decisions\n95: \n96: ### 使用 code-generator 生成客户端\n97: \n98: **选择**: 使用 Kubernetes 官方的 code-generator 工具\n99: \n100: **理由**:\n101: - 官方维护，稳定可靠\n102: - 与 Kubernetes API 版本同步\n103: - 支持所有 Kubernetes API 特性\n104: - 广泛使用，社区成熟\n105: \n106: **示例**:\n107: ```bash\n108: go run k8s.io/code-generator/cmd/client-gen \\\n109:   --input-base=\"github.com/agentcube/apis\" \\\n110:   --input=\"runtime/v1alpha1\" \\\n111:   --clientset-path=\"github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/client\"\n112: ```\n113: \n114: ### 包结构组织\n115: \n116: **选择**: 遵循 Kubernetes client-go 标准包结构\n117: \n118: **理由**:\n119: - 与 Kubernetes 生态保持一致\n120: - 便于开发者理解和使用\n121: - 支持未来扩展\n122: \n123: **包结构**:\n124: ```\n125: client-go/\n126: ├── pkg/\n127: │   ├── apis/\n128: │   │   └── runtime/\n129: │   │       └── v1alpha1/\n130: │   │           ├── doc.go\n131: │   │           ├── register.go\n132: │   │           ├── types.go\n133: │   │           ├── agentruntime_types.go\n134: │   │           └── codeinterpreter_types.go\n135: │   ├── client/\n136: │   │   ├── clientset/\n137: │   │   │   └── versioned/\n138: │   │   │       ├── clientset.go\n139: │   │   │       ├── doc.go\n140: │   │   │       ├── fake/\n141: │   │   │       └── typed/\n142: │   │   │           └── runtime/\n143: │   │   │               └── v1alpha1/\n144: │   │   │                   ├── agentruntime.go\n145: │   │   │                   ├── codeinterpreter.go\n146: │   │   │                   ├── fake/\n147: │   │   │                   │   ├── agentruntime.go\n148: │   │   │                   │   └── codeinterpreter.go\n149: │   │   │                   ├── generated_expansion.go\n150: │   │   │                   └── runtime_client.go\n151: │   ├── informers/\n152: │   │   └── externalversions/\n153: │   │       ├── internalinterfaces/\n154: │   │       └── runtime/\n155: │   │           └── v1alpha1/\n156: │   │               ├── agentruntime.go\n157: │   │               ├── codeinterpreter.go\n158: │   │               └── interface.go\n159: │   └── listers/\n160: │       └── runtime/\n161: │           └── v1alpha1/\n162: │               ├── agentruntime.go\n163: │               └── codeinterpreter.go\n164: ├── go.mod\n165: ├── go.sum\n166: ├── Makefile\n167: └── README.md\n168: ```\n169: \n170: ### API Group 和 Version 命名\n171: \n172: **选择**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n173: \n174: **理由**:\n175: - 遵循 Kubernetes API group 命名约定\n176: - `runtime` 表示运行时相关资源\n177: - `agentcube.volcano.sh` 表示 AgentCube 项目域名\n178: - `v1alpha1` 表示初始 API 版本\n179: \n180: ### 自动化代码生成\n181: \n182: **选择**: 使用 Makefile 自动化代码生成流程\n183: \n184: **理由**:\n185: - 标准化代码生成流程\n186: - 易于集成到 CI/CD\n187: - 确保代码与 CRD 定义同步\n188: \n189: **Makefile 示例**:\n190: ```makefile\n191: CODEGEN_PKG := $(shell go env GOPATH)/pkg/mod/k8s.io/code-generator@$(shell go list -m -f '{{.Version}}' k8s.io/code-generator)\n192: \n193: generate: codegen\n194: \t@echo \"Generation complete\"\n195: \n196: codegen:\n197: \t@echo \"Generating client code...\"\n198: \tgo run $(CODEGEN_PKG)/cmd/client-gen/main.go \\\n199: \t\t--input-base=github.com/agentcube/apis \\\n200: \t\t--input=runtime/v1alpha1 \\\n201: \t\t--clientset-path=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/client \\\n202: \t\t--input-dirs=github.com/agentcube/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\n203: \n204: \tgo run $(CODEGEN_PKG)/cmd/informer-gen/main.go \\\n205: \t\t--input-dirs=github.com/agentcube/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 \\\n206: \t\t--versioned-clientset-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/client/clientset/versioned \\\n207: \t\t--listers-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/listers \\\n208: \t\t--output-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/informers \\\n209: \t\t--output-base=.\n210: \n211: \tgo run $(CODEGEN_PKG)/cmd/lister-gen/main.go \\\n212: \t\t--input-dirs=github.com/agentcube/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 \\\n213: \t\t--output-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/listers\n214: ```\n215: \n216: ## Alternatives Considered\n217: \n218: ### Alternative 1: 手动编写客户端代码\n219: \n220: **描述**: 手动编写所有客户端代码\n221: \n222: **优点**:\n223: - 完全控制代码实现\n224: - 可以自定义优化\n225: \n226: **缺点**:\n227: - 维护成本高\n228: - 容易出错\n229: - 难以与 CRD 定义同步\n230: - 违反 DRY 原则\n231: \n232: **选择**: 不采纳 - 使用 code-generator 自动生成\n233: \n234: ### Alternative 2: 使用其他代码生成工具\n235: \n236: **描述**: 使用 kubebuilder 或 operator-framework 的代码生成\n237: \n238: **优点**:\n239: - 与 Controller-Runtime 集成\n240: - 提供更多高级功能\n241: \n242: **缺点**:\n243: - 引入额外依赖\n244: - 可能过于重量级\n245: - 生成的代码可能不符合我们的需求\n246: \n247: **选择**: 不采纳 - 使用轻量级的 code-generator\n248: \n249: ### Alternative 3: 直接使用 REST API\n250: \n251: **描述**: 不生成类型化客户端，直接使用 REST API\n252: \n253: **优点**:\n254: - 无需生成代码\n255: - 语言无关\n256: \n257: **缺点**:\n258: - 缺乏类型安全\n259: - 开发效率低\n260: - 容易出错\n261: - 无法利用编译时检查\n262: \n263: **选择**: 不采纳 - 类型安全对 Go 项目至关重要\n264: \n265: ## Implementation Plan\n266: \n267: ### Phase 1: 项目初始化 (Day 1)\n268: \n269: 1. 创建 client-go 目录结构\n270: 2. 初始化 Go module\n271: 3. 配置 go.mod 依赖\n272: 4. 创建基础目录\n273: 5. 设置 Makefile\n274: \n275: **检查清单**:\n276: - [ ] 目录结构创建\n277: - [ ] Go module 初始化\n278: - [ ] 依赖配置\n279: - [ ] Makefile 创建\n280: \n281: ### Phase 2: API 类型定义 (Day 1-2)\n282: \n283: 1. 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 目录\n284: 2. 定义 doc.go\n285: 3. 定义 register.go\n286: 4. 定义 types.go\n287: 5. 定义 AgentRuntime 类型\n288: 6. 定义 CodeInterpreter 类型\n289: \n290: **检查清单**:\n291: - [ ] doc.go 创建\n292: - [ ] register.go 创建\n293: - [ ] types.go 创建\n294: - [ ] AgentRuntime 类型定义\n295: - [ ] CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n296: \n297: ### Phase 3: 代码生成配置 (Day 2)\n298: \n299: 1. 配置 code-generator 参数\n300: 2. 创建代码生成脚本\n301: 3. 配置 Makefile 目标\n302: 4. 测试代码生成\n303: \n304: **检查清单**:\n305: - [ ] code-generator 配置\n306: - [ ] 生成脚本创建\n307: - [ ] Makefile 目标配置\n308: - [ ] 代码生成测试\n309: \n310: ### Phase 4: ClientSet 生成 (Day 2-3)\n311: \n312: 1. 生成 clientset 代码\n313: 2. 验证生成的接口\n314: 3. 测试 CRUD 操作\n315: 4. 测试 namespace-scoped 操作\n316: \n317: **检查清单**:\n318: - [ ] clientset 生成\n319: - [ ] 接口验证\n320: - [ ] CRUD 测试\n321: - [ ] namespace 测试\n322: \n323: ### Phase 5: Informer 生成 (Day 3-4)\n324: \n325: 1. 生成 informer 代码\n326: 2. 实现 AgentRuntime informer\n327: 3. 实现 CodeInterpreter informer\n328: 4. 测试事件处理\n329: \n330: **检查清单**:\n331: - [ ] informer 生成\n332: - [ ] AgentRuntime informer\n333: - [ ] CodeInterpreter informer\n334: - [ ] 事件处理测试\n335: \n336: ### Phase 6: Lister 生成 (Day 4)\n337: \n338: 1. 生成 lister 代码\n339: 2. 实现 AgentRuntime lister\n340: 3. 实现 CodeInterpreter lister\n341: 4. 测试只读访问\n342: \n343: **检查清单**:\n344: - [ ] lister 生成\n345: - [ ] AgentRuntime lister\n346: - [ ] CodeInterpreter lister\n347: - [ ] 只读访问测试\n348: \n349: ### Phase 7: 测试和验证 (Day 4-5)\n350: \n351: 1. 编写单元测试\n352: 2. 编写集成测试\n353: 3. 测试所有 API 操作\n354: 4. 测试错误处理\n355: 5. 性能测试\n356: \n357: **检查清单**:\n358: - [ ] 单元测试\n359: - [ ] 集成测试\n360: - [ ] API 测试\n361: - [ ] 错误处理测试\n362: - [ ] 性能测试\n363: \n364: ### Phase 8: 文档和示例 (Day 5)\n365: \n366: 1. 编写 README.md\n367: 2. 编写 API 文档\n368: 3. 创建使用示例\n369: 4. 编写最佳实践指南\n370: \n371: **检查清单**:\n372: - [ ] README.md\n373: - [ ] API 文档\n374: - [ ] 使用示例\n375: - [ ] 最佳实践指南\n376: \n377: ### Phase 9: CI/CD 集成 (Day 5-6)\n378: \n379: 1. 配置 CI pipeline\n380: 2. 自动化代码生成\n381: 3. 自动化测试\n382: 4. 发布流程\n383: \n384: **检查清单**:\n385: - [ ] CI 配置\n386: - [ ] 自动化生成\n387: - [ ] 自动化测试\n388: - [ ] 发布流程\n389: \n390: ## Testing Strategy\n391: \n392: ### Unit Tests\n393: \n394: 1. **Client 测试**\n395:    - 测试 CRUD 操作\n396:    - 测试错误处理\n397:    - 测试参数验证\n398: \n399: 2. **Informer 测试**\n400:    - 测试事件触发\n401:    - 测试缓存更新\n402:    - 测试处理器注册\n403: \n404: 3. **Lister 测试**\n405:    - 测试资源查询\n406:    - 测试缓存命中\n407:    - 测试 namespace 过滤\n408: \n409: ### Integration Tests\n410: \n411: 1. **ClientSet 集成测试**\n412:    - 连接真实 Kubernetes 集群\n413:    - 测试完整 CRUD 流程\n414:    - 测试并发操作\n415: \n416: 2. **Informer 集成测试**\n417:    - 测试实时事件监听\n418:    - 测试多客户端同步\n419:    - 测试重连机制\n420: \n421: 3. **Lister 集成测试**\n422:    - 测试大规模资源查询\n423:    - 测试缓存一致性\n424:    - 测试性能指标\n425: \n426: ### End-to-End Tests\n427: \n428: 1. **完整工作流测试**\n429:    - 创建资源\n430:    - Watch 资源变更\n431:    - 更新资源\n432:    - 删除资源\n433: \n434: 2. **错误恢复测试**\n435:    - 测试网络故障\n436:    - 测试 API 服务器故障\n437:    - 测试重连机制\n438: \n439: 3. **性能测试**\n440:    - 测试高并发场景\n441:    - 测试大规模资源操作\n442:    - 测试内存使用\n443: \n444: ## API Specification\n445: \n446: ### AgentRuntime Client API\n447: \n448: ```go\n449: type AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n450:     Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n451:     Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n452:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n453:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n454:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n455:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n456:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n457:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n458:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (result *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, err error)\n459: }\n460: ```\n461: \n462: ### CodeInterpreter Client API\n463: \n464: ```go\n465: type CodeInterpreterInterface interface {\n466:     Create(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n467:     Update(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n468:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n469:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n470:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n471:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n472:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList, error)\n473:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n474:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (result *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, err error)\n475: }\n476: ```\n477: \n478: ## Configuration\n479: \n480: ### Go Module 配置\n481: \n482: ```go\n483: module github.com/agentcube/client-go\n484: \n485: go 1.19\n486: \n487: require (\n488:     k8s.io/api v0.26.0\n489:     k8s.io/apimachinery v0.26.0\n490:     k8s.io/client-go v0.26.0\n491:     k8s.io/code-generator v0.26.0\n492: )\n493: ```\n494: \n495: ## Security Considerations\n496: \n497: 1. **身份验证**\n498:    - 支持 kubeconfig 配置\n499:    - 支持 ServiceAccount token\n500:    - 支持 TLS 证书\n501: \n502: 2. **授权**\n503:    - 遵循 Kubernetes RBAC\n504:    - 权限检查\n505:    - 审计日志\n506: \n507: 3. **数据安全**\n508:    - 敏感数据加密\n509:    - 安全的日志记录\n510:    - 错误信息脱敏\n511: \n512: ## Performance Considerations\n513: \n514: 1. **缓存策略**\n515:    - Informer 本地缓存\n516:    - 高效的缓存更新\n517:    - 缓存一致性保证\n518: \n519: 2. **并发控制**\n520:    - 连接池管理\n521:    - 请求限流\n522:    - 并发安全\n523: \n524: 3. **资源使用**\n525:    - 内存优化\n526:    - Goroutine 管理\n527:    - 连接复用\n528: \n529: ## Monitoring and Metrics\n530: \n531: ### 关键指标\n532: \n533: 1. **客户端指标**\n534:    - API 调用延迟\n535:    - API 调用成功率\n536:    - API 调用频率\n537: \n538: 2. **Informer 指标**\n539:    - 事件处理延迟\n540:    - 缓存命中率\n541:    - 同步状态\n542: \n543: 3. **Lister 指标**\n544:    - 查询延迟\n545:    - 缓存大小\n546:    - 查询频率\n547: \n548: ## Success Criteria\n549: \n550: - 成功生成完整的 client-go 客户端库\n551: - 所有 CRUD 操作正常工作\n552: - Informer 和 Lister 功能完善\n553: - 测试覆盖率达到 80% 以上\n554: - 文档完整清晰\n555: - 示例代码可用\n556: - CI/CD 集成完成\n557: \n558: ## References\n559: \n560: - [Kubernetes client-go Documentation](https://github.com/kubernetes/client-go)\n561: - [Kubernetes code-generator](https://github.com/kubernetes/code-generator)\n562: - [AgentCube Spec](../../spec.md)\n563: - [AR-035 Spec](./spec.md)\n564: - [Kubernetes API Conventions](https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md)\n\n(End of file - total 564 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-035: client-go 类型客户端生成\n\n## Overview\n\n为 AgentCube 平台生成基于 Kubernetes client-go 的类型化客户端库，提供对自定义资源（AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter 等）的强类型 API 访问能力，支持 CRUD 操作、Watch 机制和 Informer 模式。\n\n## Purpose\n\nclient-go 类型客户端是 AgentCube 平台开发者工具链的核心组成部分，旨在：\n\n1. **类型安全** - 提供编译时类型检查，避免运行时错误\n2. **开发效率** - 简化 Kubernetes API 调用，提供简洁的开发体验\n3. **标准化接口** - 遵循 Kubernetes client-go 最佳实践和约定\n4. **高性能** - 支持高效的 Watch 和 Informer 机制\n5. **可维护性** - 自动生成客户端代码，与 CRD 定义保持同步\n\n## Module\n\n`client-go` - Go 客户端库\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775887226869,"end":1775887226880}}}}
