{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775887234382,"sessionID":"ses_284dfe4edffeXF09uj2DLyG8WE","part":{"id":"prt_d7b20b548001NrmHHBIJZhMx1J","messageID":"msg_d7b20a9d1001jAvgj8wtTO3383","sessionID":"ses_284dfe4edffeXF09uj2DLyG8WE","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775887413119,"sessionID":"ses_284dfe4edffeXF09uj2DLyG8WE","part":{"id":"prt_d7b236ee3001HBJolNyD5XE7IW","messageID":"msg_d7b20a9d1001jAvgj8wtTO3383","sessionID":"ses_284dfe4edffeXF09uj2DLyG8WE","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-a54a919b7fc04ecda7564d22bafd1fe2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 Design\n\n## AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成\n\n**Module**: `client-go`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: L\n**Purpose**: Generate a type-safe Kubernetes client-go library for AgentCube custom resources (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter), providing typed API access with CRUD operations, Watch mechanism, and Informer pattern support.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Package Structure\n\n```\nclient-go/\n├── clientset/\n│   └── versioned/\n│       ├── clientset.go                    # Clientset, Interface, constructors\n│       ├── doc.go                          # Package documentation\n│       ├── scheme/\n│       │   ├── doc.go                      # Scheme documentation\n│       │   └── register.go                 # Scheme / codecs for generated client\n│       ├── fake/\n│       │   ├── clientset_generated.go      # Fake clientset implementation\n│       │   ├── doc.go                      # Fake clientset documentation\n│       │   └── register.go                 # Fake scheme wiring\n│       └── typed/\n│           └── runtime/\n│               └── v1alpha1/\n│                   ├── runtime_client.go    # RuntimeV1alpha1Client, RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n│                   ├── agentruntime.go      # AgentRuntimeInterface, typed REST client\n│                   ├── codeinterpreter.go   # CodeInterpreterInterface, typed REST client\n│                   ├── generated_expansion.go # Expansion interfaces\n│                   ├── doc.go               # Documentation\n│                   └── fake/\n│                       ├── fake_runtime_client.go  # Fake runtime group client\n│                       ├── fake_agentruntime.go    # Fake AgentRuntime client\n│                       ├── fake_codeinterpreter.go # Fake CodeInterpreter client\n│                       └── doc.go                    # Documentation\n├── informers/\n│   └── externalversions/\n│       ├── factory.go                      # SharedInformerFactory, options, Start/Shutdown/WaitForCacheSync\n│       ├── generic.go                      # GenericInformer, ForResource\n│       ├── internalinterfaces/\n│       │   └── factory_interfaces.go       # Small factory interface + NewInformerFunc, TweakListOptionsFunc\n│       └── runtime/\n│           ├── interface.go                # Group runtime informer accessor\n│           └── v1alpha1/\n│               ├── interface.go            # v1alpha1 informer accessors\n│               ├── agentruntime.go         # AgentRuntime informer + constructor\n│               └── codeinterpreter.go      # CodeInterpreter informer + constructor\n├── listers/\n│   └── runtime/\n│       └── v1alpha1/\n│           ├── agentruntime.go             # AgentRuntimeLister, namespace lister\n│           ├── codeinterpreter.go          # CodeInterpreterLister, namespace lister\n│           └── expansion_generated.go     # Lister expansion interfaces\n├── go.mod                                   # Go module definition\n├── go.sum                                   # Go dependencies\n└── README.md                                # Usage documentation\n```\n\n### Component Interactions\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Application / Controller                    │\n│                                                                  │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │                      ClientSet                           │  │\n│  │  NewForConfig(cfg) → *Clientset                          │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│                            │                                    │\n│                            ▼                                    │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │              RuntimeV1alpha1Interface                    │  │\n│  │  clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1() → RuntimeV1alpha1Interface  │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│                            │                                    │\n│              ┌─────────────┴─────────────┐                    │\n│              ▼                           ▼                    │\n│  ┌──────────────────────┐   ┌──────────────────────┐        │\n│  │ AgentRuntimeInterface│   │CodeInterpreterInterf │        │\n│  │ .AgentRuntimes(ns)   │   │.CodeInterpreters(ns) │        │\n│  └──────────────────────┘   └──────────────────────┘        │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                            │                                    │\n                            │ REST API (Kubernetes API Server)  │\n                            ▼                                    │\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                   Kubernetes API Server                        │\n│                                                                  │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │     runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1               │  │\n│  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n│  │  │  agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh        │  │  │\n│  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │  │\n│  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n│  │  │  codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh     │  │  │\n│  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                SharedInformerFactory (Event-driven)             │\n│                                                                  │\n│  NewSharedInformerFactory(client, resync) → factory             │\n│                            │                                    │\n│              ┌─────────────┴─────────────┐                    │\n│              ▼                           ▼                    │\n│  ┌──────────────────────┐   ┌──────────────────────┐        │\n│  │ AgentRuntimeInformer │   │CodeInterpreterInfor. │        │\n│  │ factory.Runtime()   │   │factory.Runtime()   │        │\n│  │  .V1alpha1()         │   │  .V1alpha1()         │        │\n│  │  .AgentRuntimes()    │   │  .CodeInterpreters() │        │\n│  └──────────────────────┘   └──────────────────────┘        │\n│         │                              │                     │\n│         ▼                              ▼                     │\n│  ┌──────────────────┐      ┌──────────────────┐             │\n│  │ AgentRuntimeList │      │CodeInterpreterLis│             │\n│  │ er               │      │ ter               │             │\n│  └──────────────────┘      └──────────────────┘             │\n│                                                                  │\n│  Event Handlers:                                                │\n│  - AddFunc(obj)                                                 │\n│  - UpdateFunc(oldObj, newObj)                                  │\n│  - DeleteFunc(obj)                                              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### Clientset Structure\n\n**File**: `clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n\n```go\n// Interface defines the clientset interface\ntype Interface interface {\n    Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n    RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n}\n\n// Clientset contains the clients for groups.\ntype Clientset struct {\n    *discovery.DiscoveryClient\n    runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client\n}\n\n// NewForConfig creates a new Clientset for the given config.\nfunc NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error) {\n    configShallowCopy := *c\n    if configShallowCopy.RateLimiter == nil && configShallowCopy.QPS > 0 {\n        if configShallowCopy.Burst <= 0 {\n            return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"burst is required to be greater than 0 when RateLimiter is not set and QPS is set to greater than 0\")\n        }\n        configShallowCopy.RateLimiter = flowcontrol.NewTokenBucketRateLimiter(configShallowCopy.QPS, configShallowCopy.Burst)\n    }\n    var cs Clientset\n    var err error\n    cs.runtimeV1alpha1, err = runtimev1alpha1.NewForConfig(&configShallowCopy)\n    if err != nil {\n        return nil, err\n    }\n    cs.DiscoveryClient, err = discovery.NewDiscoveryClientForConfig(&configShallowCopy)\n    if err != nil {\n        return nil, err\n    }\n    return &cs, nil\n}\n\n// NewForConfigAndClient creates a new Clientset for the given config and http client.\nfunc NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error) {\n    configShallowCopy := *c\n    if configShallowCopy.RateLimiter == nil && configShallowCopy.QPS > 0 {\n        if configShallowCopy.Burst <= 0 {\n            return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"burst is required to be greater than 0 when RateLimiter is not set and QPS is set to greater than 0\")\n        }\n        configShallowCopy.RateLimiter = flowcontrol.NewTokenBucketRateLimiter(configShallowCopy.QPS, configShallowCopy.Burst)\n    }\n    var cs Clientset\n    var err error\n    cs.runtimeV1alpha1, err = runtimev1alpha1.NewForConfigAndClient(&configShallowCopy, httpClient)\n    if err != nil {\n        return nil, err\n    }\n    cs.DiscoveryClient, err = discovery.NewDiscoveryClientForConfigAndClient(&configShallowCopy, httpClient)\n    if err != nil {\n        return nil, err\n    }\n    return &cs, nil\n}\n\n// NewForConfigOrDie creates a new Clientset for the given config and panics if there is an error in the config.\nfunc NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset {\n    var cs Clientset\n    cs.runtimeV1alpha1 = runtimev1alpha1.NewForConfigOrDie(c)\n    cs.DiscoveryClient = discovery.NewDiscoveryClientForConfigOrDie(c)\n    return &cs\n}\n\n// New creates a new Clientset for the given RESTClient.\nfunc New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset {\n    var cs Clientset\n    cs.runtimeV1alpha1 = runtimev1alpha1.New(c)\n    cs.DiscoveryClient = discovery.NewDiscoveryClient(c)\n    return &cs\n}\n\n// RuntimeV1alpha1 retrieves the RuntimeV1alpha1Client\nfunc (c *Clientset) RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface {\n    return c.runtimeV1alpha1\n}\n```\n\n### RuntimeV1alpha1 Typed Client\n\n**File**: `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`\n\n```go\n// RuntimeV1alpha1Client is used to interact with features provided by the runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh group.\ntype RuntimeV1alpha1Client struct {\n    restClient rest.Interface\n}\n\n// NewForConfig creates a new RuntimeV1alpha1Client for the given config.\nfunc NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*RuntimeV1alpha1Client, error) {\n    config := *c\n    if err := setConfigDefaults(&config); err != nil {\n        return nil, err\n    }\n    client, err := rest.RESTClientFor(&config)\n    if err != nil {\n        return nil, err\n    }\n    return &RuntimeV1alpha1Client{client}, nil\n}\n\n// NewForConfigAndClient creates a new RuntimeV1alpha1Client for the given config and HTTP client.\nfunc NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*RuntimeV1alpha1Client, error) {\n    config := *c\n    if err := setConfigDefaults(&config); err != nil {\n        return nil, err\n    }\n    client, err := rest.RESTClientForConfigAndClient(&config, httpClient)\n    if err != nil {\n        return nil, err\n    }\n    return &RuntimeV1alpha1Client{client}, nil\n}\n\n// NewForConfigOrDie creates a new RuntimeV1alpha1Client for the given config and panics if there is an error in the config.\nfunc NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *RuntimeV1alpha1Client {\n    client, err := NewForConfig(c)\n    if err != nil {\n        panic(err)\n    }\n    return client\n}\n\n// New creates a new RuntimeV1alpha1Client for the given RESTClient.\nfunc New(c rest.Interface) *RuntimeV1alpha1Client {\n    return &RuntimeV1alpha1Client{c}\n}\n\n// setConfigDefaults sets default values on the provided client config.\nfunc setConfigDefaults(config *rest.Config) error {\n    gvk := schema.GroupVersionKind{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n    config.GroupVersion = &schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n    config.APIPath = \"/apis\"\n    config.NegotiatedSerializer = scheme.Codecs.WithoutConversion()\n    if config.UserAgent == \"\" {\n        config.UserAgent = rest.DefaultKubernetesUserAgent()\n    }\n    return nil\n}\n\n// RESTClient returns a RESTClient that is used to communicate with API server by this client implementation.\nfunc (c *RuntimeV1alpha1Client) RESTClient() rest.Interface {\n    if c == nil {\n        return nil\n    }\n    return c.restClient\n}\n```\n\n### AgentRuntime Interface\n\n**File**: `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n\n```go\n// AgentRuntimesGetter has a method to return a AgentRuntimeInterface.\ntype AgentRuntimesGetter interface {\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n}\n\n// AgentRuntimeInterface has methods to work with AgentRuntime resources.\ntype AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*v1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agent